      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for a great new home. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape, both inside and out. It drives like a dream and has plenty of life left in it! If you're looking for a dependable car that's been well-loved and is ready for the road, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
