    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example features a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis is enhanced with Bilstein dampers and a documented rear subframe reinforcement, addressing key structural concerns. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing service, ensuring mechanical longevity. Finished with staggered Style 67 alloys and Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires, this car delivers the tactile steering feedback and balanced dynamics the chassis is renowned for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
