      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for, dependable driver. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, showing only the minor, superficial stone chips one would expect from a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been kept in a smoke-free environment; the seats are firm and the upholstery shows minimal wear. All power features, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has benefited from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule. It has recently passed a comprehensive safety inspection and sits on tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, honest vehicle that delivers a premium driving experience without the premium price tag.",
